title: Banking sector in good financial health to support growth: RBI dy guv
description: The banking sector in India has reached a decadal high in terms of financial parameters and is poised to support the country's economic growth, said Reserve Bank deputy governor Swaminathan J on Tuesday. He was speaking at a conference attended by statutory auditors, chief financial officers of commercial banks, and all Indian financial institutions.
